Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.ticket_manager.model.command.Command
  • public class Command
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates objects that encapsulates user actions (or transitions) that cause the state of a Ticket to update. This description is derived from the instructions' Implementation section.
